persons:
    person-mycah:
        properties:
            name:
                value: "Mycah"
                fields:
                    given: "Mycah"
            gender: male
        notes: "Butcher's boy traveling with the Stark party from Winterfell to King's Landing. Befriended Arya Stark and practiced sword-fighting with sticks near the Trident. Joffrey Baratheon cut his cheek with Lion's Tooth when he refused to fight. Arya attacked Joffrey to protect Mycah. Mycah fled into the trees; Sandor Clegane pursued and killed him, cutting him nearly in half 'from shoulder to waist.' His body was returned slung over the Hound's destrier."
